songs.title: Don Quan Intro (2016)
songs.lyrics:
[Spoken Word: Don Quan]
Man, what the hell going on? It's Don Quan, man
I know y'all folks been waitin' on this shit, but y'all ain't gotta wait no more, you know?
First, we killed you with the Pimpin' Ain't Easy, then we killed you with the Glocks and Thots
Now with the SANDAS, suck a nigga dick or somethin', you know?
All that type of shit, man, believe it
